### Health Check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Create a new Indicator
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/indicators
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "indicator_type": "IP",
    "value": "8.8.8.8",
    "severity": "low",
    "source": "Google DNS",
    "confidence": 25
}

### List all Indicators
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/indicators

### Paginated indicators with ETag and total-count headers
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/indicators/page?page=1&page_size=5

### CSV export
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/indicators/export.csv

### Get specific Indicator (ID 1)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/indicators/1
